{"tid":1281192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致仍然想以死相諫巴絲嘅一封信","createTime":"2019-07-03T08:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T10:03:21.000Z","uid":29006,"like":104,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"18711c1059920850af5005a12551430345fbcccd","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:20:44.000Z","msg":"致仍然想以死相諫巴絲嘅一封信：<br />\n<br />\n經過修例以嚟嘅種種風波同行動，相信你同我都一樣好攰，可能你同我一樣都覺得做過嘅事好似徒勞無功咁，所以咁可能我地都突然彈出一個「唔想撐落去」嘅念頭，當呢個念頭產生，有人選擇離開現場返屋企瞓覺休息、有人選擇離開香港去吓旅行、有人選擇離開呢個世界嚟控訴政府。<br />\n<br />\n當你攰嘅時候，不妨睇多幾次立場姐姐同義士妹妹冒死入議事廳救人嘅對話，「贏就一齊贏，輸就一齊輸」唔係一句口號，係咁多個喺唔同崗位巴絲作出嘅一個有效承諾。文宣組漏夜整圖、行動組計劃路線、仲有唔同巴絲都出盡辦法協助呢場運動，為嘅係想喺有一日我哋可以贏，可以一刻間掃走晒呢幾個月嚟嘅委屈。<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔敢講好愛你，但一定係好關心，好重視我哋每一個人。當一有巴絲話想以離開做最後嘅吶喊，我哋會發晒茅，癲晒咁咁走圍出Post、動員咁去搵你，為嘅只係想喺有一日可以捉住你隻手一吓舉高，享受勝利嘅暢快。應承我哋，陪我哋一齊奮鬥，好唔好？"},{"pid":"c4f7574597304d7ddaf24706a467cc602346676e","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"推，好想畀所有有呢個念頭嘅巴打絲打睇到"},{"pid":"6f12d5a6893ca034c612260287f15959df470045","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32f3ebfeb7feb223c855aa291085d45147448774","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd4a69332142b272653eb165bd5fe94a912c8bb9","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a2a27f33858191f4bcd56d20ceac9b47e956525","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"843abef8fad57e676baedd4cd356e40c4df2210a","tid":1281192,"uid":103861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ca0bdacaa4f06bcca483b3138c0c5bad48fb74b7","tid":1281192,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"459dac51f9d7f0ce708527cc19f14edc28b98107","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"843abef8fad57e676baedd4cd356e40c4df2210a","tid":1281192,"uid":103861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:23:06.000Z","msg":"感謝，好想全部人一齊贏"},{"pid":"443e778dc65aadb568bd0f3540c89aaee24636a5","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a71fa40b88384841b89ccf2a79a512a592c2c09f","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd48b786849a1985bfae6e92ea8788d121643b56","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:23:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6397a9c10e2aa6d7451ca50ab62771d01cc5d70e","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05f7677966e34aaa6197932fc11dabe001ec1b4b","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f76db839ed03dfe8c32c71f2d478c95b8a1fd08d","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebc2d4ce3b60035dbf30d82f1d8a8ffae8b1b222","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6272ca76685cf5b8e1cdecf0143d12591644449","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:26:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65439aaee527f088cbf3d7748082ee9b1240435d","tid":1281192,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"72ecb44066013d0034d0fd057c094b63143c2249","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec437dbc52800317b7d69fec44e2f45fee8581f3","tid":1281192,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9S9CYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9S9CYx.jpg&h=0e742cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUVjfLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUVjfLe.jpg&h=ffda8ee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87702d0f0dce1fb2edb61562efe1c9866f40adf3","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72e2d9fe2c57257b6857031c58ebe118461728da","tid":1281192,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:27:40.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打唔洗灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要明白呢個歷史規律，喺大家都有去為民主自由而努力嘅前題之下，其實係一定會贏，只係我地唔知道幾時先會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個過程仲好可能會好漫長同有好多挫折。但最後一定會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解呢？原因好簡單，因為呢個係人類歷史發展嘅必然趨勢，舉個例，起初人類係原始部落社會，居住族群越嚟越大，慢慢出現唔同文明、秩序、分工、經濟，後來就演變成封建君主專制社會，由皇帝皇室為核心，以君主至上或者上帝嘅名義以極權去管治國家<br />\n<br />\n後來歐洲啟蒙之後神權至上受到挑戰，慢慢衝破思想框框，思想同科技得以進步，後來民主思潮萌生，將世上一個又一個君主專制政權推倒，最後席捲全球<br />\n<br />\n所以全球民主化其實係歷史發展嘅必然，前題係必須大家都要去為民主自由而努力，正如呢幾百年嘅人一樣，冇佢地嘅努力都唔會令民主得以喺世界擴散"},{"pid":"8bab482a10a67a4ef5e35dbd615134e432fcf57c","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65439aaee527f088cbf3d7748082ee9b1240435d","tid":1281192,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d598bc579dded328cbb6499c89720c78ed6c4608","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72e2d9fe2c57257b6857031c58ebe118461728da","tid":1281192,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:27:40.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打唔洗灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要明白呢個歷史規律，喺大家都有去為民主自由而努力嘅前題之下，其實係一定會贏，只係我地唔知道幾時先會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個過程仲好可能會好漫長同有好多挫折。但最後一定會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解呢？原因好簡單，因為呢個係人類歷史發展嘅必然趨勢，舉個例，起初人類係原始部落社會，居住族群越嚟越大，慢慢出現唔同文明、秩序、分工、經濟，後來就演變成封建君主專制社會，由皇帝皇室為核心，以君主至上或者上帝嘅名義以極權去管治國家<br />\n<br />\n後來歐洲啟蒙之後神權至上受到挑戰，慢慢衝破思想框框，思想同科技得以進步，後來民主思潮萌生，將世上一個又一個君主專制政權推倒，最後席捲全球<br />\n<br />\n所以全球民主化其實係歷史發展嘅必然，前題係必須大家都要去為民主自由而努力，正如呢幾百年嘅人一樣，冇佢地嘅努力都唔會令民主得以喺世界擴散"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"係，每一頁世界歷史都話畀大家知，贏唔係一時三刻嘅事，陳勝吳廣只係第一步"},{"pid":"335e5c5a0aebff271ca4caec0127217d220df8c6","tid":1281192,"uid":258484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n唔好再話人懦弱啊屌你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1280860\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1280860</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1692868c22676a3bf095ed005773f5896acaef79","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"335e5c5a0aebff271ca4caec0127217d220df8c6","tid":1281192,"uid":258484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n唔好再話人懦弱啊屌你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1280860\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1280860</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:30:11.000Z","msg":"好同意，唔可以譴有去意嘅人，我哋都一樣係受壓迫嘅一群人"},{"pid":"65a8e9ecdb7d436577cf8f6684584a3c75876b6a","tid":1281192,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:30:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae6